node.text: what’s good yall! it’s Chase Hudson—the real me. i know you’ve been wondering why i changed my name… that’s cause i’m keeping it real from yours truly with the #KeepItRealMeals @burgerking featuring a Spicy Ch’King sandwich and Mozzarella Sticks as well as a Chocolate Shake. this meal is just so real, i had to name it after my real self.🖤 Starting 9.13 in the U.S. only. Learn more at bk.com/realmeals #ad
